public enum DDF_Indicator
extends Enum<DDF_Indicator>
implements com.barchart.util.enums.EnumCodeString, com.barchart.util.enums.EnumByteOrdinal

ddf quote session indicator : "current combo" vs "previous combo" vs "individual session"; possible format: "combined", is combo for today; "previous", is combo for yesterday; "session_D_S", individual (non-combo) day/session permutations; with D=DDF_TradeDay, S=DDF_Session; allows to classify quote snapshot sessions: THIS vs PAST market day.
